   Forest Ranger  Hugo Danner  Knight Lightning  Lex Luthor \n     Lucifer 666 ParMaster  Phil Free  Predat0r  Rabbit \n     Stephan  Synthetic Slug
                         Taran King  Tuc  The Urvile

